/* /////////////////////////////////////////////////////

Dedicated stylesheet for the in-Canvas LTI iframe views (lti_iframe layout).

These are minimal, chrome-less pages embedded in a small Canvas iframe. They
must NOT pull in the whole dashboard: the `main` bundle plus its external
Google Fonts and the app JS (vendors, i18n, Sentry) made the iframe load
slowly and flash unstyled text while the webfont swapped in.

So this bundle cherry-picks only the foundation (reset + shared variables/
mixins + icons + layout + base) and the three component modules the iframe
views actually use — buttons (_controls), .module (_modules), and the LTI
iframe module — instead of `@import "modules/*"`. Fonts fall back to the
system/arial stack (no external webfont request, no swap).

///////////////////////////////////////////////////// */
@import "_reset"
@import "_shared"
@import "_icons"
@import "_layout"
@import "_base"
@import "modules/_controls"
@import "modules/_modules"
@import "modules/_lti_iframe"
